			<link>https://www.brahmakumaris.org#comment-1982</link>
			<description><![CDATA[Yumii:  Being peaceful, which is our true nature, is a light and joyful experience and doesn't mean that we have to sit in one place and be still.  Because we are connected to the truth that we really are the soul is full and content.  Being peaceful makes us powerful and strong because we are then able to face life in a calm and stable way and see things clearly without getting affected by others behavior  We have the patience and the love to understand them, and uplift them.  Being peaceful allows us to enjoy the wonder of this world without getting attached to things and people which will cause us sorrow.  Being peaceful is not boring . . . but gives us the ability to live life to the full and share it with others with a vision of brotherhood and love. So enjoy your peaceful life and have fun.]]></description>
