			<description><![CDATA[Sonia,  One of the aims of meditation is to bring the peace that you experience in meditation into your everyday life, so that while you look after your household, children, cook, go to work etc. you are doing it in a state of peace, which will bring happiness to yourself, to your family, and work colleagues.  Peace is our natural state of being, so connecting with this peace in meditation reminds us who we are, we can then bring that awareness into our everyday activities, perhaps see things from a different perspective, allowing us to make new choices.  So if everyone were to go into a state of peace, the world would certainly be a better place with people making peaceful more equitable choices that bring benefit to all]]></description>
